cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.CV 

The paper deals with adapting reinforcement learning algorithms to use ordinal rewards instead of numerical rewards. This falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of deep reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). Additionally, the evaluation of the proposed approach involves solving problems in the OpenAI Gym framework, which is related to robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY).
